# NEO4J_PASSWORD — Railway > neo4j service > Variables
# RAILWAY_TOKEN — railway.app > Account Settings > Tokens
# N8N_API_KEY — n8n.willbracken.com > Settings > API
# COCKROACH_DB_CONNECTION_STRING — CockroachDB Cloud dashboard
